                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Of Course -- I prayed --</l>
                    <l>And did God Care?</l>
                    <l>He cared as much as on the Air</l>
                    <l>A Bird -- had stamped her foot --</l>
                    <l>And cried "Give Me" --</l>
                    <l>My Reason -- Life --</l>
                    <l>I had not had -- but for Yourself --</l>
                    <l>'Twere better Charity</l>
                    <l>To leave me in the Atom's Tomb --</l>
                    <l>Merry, and Nought, and gay, and numb --</l>
                    <l>Than this smart Misery.</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
